#: ../../../usage/packages-in-pyodide.md:5
msgid ""
"This is the list of Python packages included with the current version of "
"Pyodide. These packages can be loaded with {js:func}`pyodide.loadPackage` or "
"{py:func}`micropip.install`. See {ref}`loading_packages` for information "
"about loading packages. Pure Python packages with wheels on PyPI can be "
"loaded directly from PyPI with {py:func}`micropip.install`."
msgstr ""
